# Intro to Cloud Computing

Traditionally company's have their own data centers that provide their digital services.

This tends to be know as: "On Premises" or "On Prem"

## Cloud Computing

Cloud Computing resources accessed over the internet on demand.

- Often has a service platform (GUI)
- Ususally pay as you go pricing
- Go global fast
- Access the cloud from anywhere
- Less to manage/maintain

## Examples of popular cloud services?

- Netflix, Prime video
- Youtube
- Google outlook

